No. 10-8150. Gary M. Cohen, Petitioner v. Federal Express Corporation. 563 U.S. 902, 131 S. Ct. 1808,

179 L. Ed. 2d 653,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 2485. March 28, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for reconsideration of order denying leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied.

Justice Sotomayor took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion.
